</div>
<div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
<p>What could they negotiate? Nothing! Only betrayal by proposing to exchange themselves in exchange for serving to infamous Chairman Gonzalo with their own treachery in order to annihilate the Party and the People’s War.</p>
<p>他们能谈判什么呢？什么都不能!能做的就是背叛，就是提出用他们自己的背信弃义，交换自己，换取为臭名昭著的贡萨罗主席服务，以消灭党和人民战争。</p>
<p>好奇怪，不知道怎么翻译。</p>
</div>
